post_text:
To D91 Parents and Caregivers;

Just a reminder that District 91 will be conducting Parent Academy Training to assist families with remote learning. Sessions will include training for Google Classroom (8/17), Illuminate Parent Portal (8/18) and Zoom (8/20). You may select either a morning (10-11 am) or evening (6-7 pm) for each session.

To learn more about Parent Academy Training dates and times and to sign up go to https://www.fpsd91.org/domain/635.

