To All Parents and Guardians;

FYI, District 91 will be collecting Chromebooks from all grade levels at the FPMS gymnasium from Monday, July 20 - Thursday, July 23, 2020. On those days, District 91 representatives will be at the FPMS gymnasium from 9-11 am only. Please enter the gym from the vestibule located on Ferdinand Avenue.

If you have any questions please contact Zack Frangidakis at zfrangidakis@fpsd91.org.

